   <title>Accessing functions by using REST APIs</title>
   <p>The functions that are available in the <ph conref="../TextEntities.dita#TextEntities/ISMgui"
            />, are accessible by using REST Administration APIs. Before you can use <ph
               conref="../TextEntities.dita#TextEntities/ISM"/>, you must accept the license
            agreement by using a REST Administration API. Until the license is accepted, the <ph
               conref="../TextEntities.dita#TextEntities/ISM"/> server remains in maintenance mode.
            For more information about using a REST Administration API to set the licensed usage and
            accept the license agreement, see <xref format="dita"
               href="../Administering/ad00793_.dita" scope="local" type="task"/>.</p>
   <p>For more information about using REST APIs and the <ph
               conref="../TextEntities.dita#TextEntities/ISMgui"/> to complete administrative tasks,
            see <xref format="dita" href="../Administering/ad00000_.dita" scope="local"
